4_s
Make a deal with the Prussians to import their advanced weapons, considered the best in Europe by many. The Dreyse Needle Gun is a new kind of breech-loading rifle, the first one to use bolt action to open and close the chamber. Krupp's C/61 6-pounder field guns are rapid-firing breech-loaders. Both weapons offer high manufacturing standards and long-range accuracy.
Dreyse Needle guns and 6-pounder Krupp Rifles import deals.


