Finance construction of heavily armed and armored ironclad gunboats. These vessels can be operated along major navigable rivers to engage enemy fortifications, which could easily obliterate the common wooden or lightly armored gunboats. The ironclad gunboats can also navigate open seas, making them versatile in naval operations.\nThe designs are quite simple, allowing construction even in mid-level (2) shipyards.
Ironclad Gunboats and Ironclad River Gunboats available.
