Finance ship designers and shipyards to allow construction of small Ironclad Gunboat Rams, that can be operated along the coasts and major navigable rivers. While the ship is small and lightly armed, the Ironclad Gunboat Ram's iron-plated and sloped casemates can withstand enemy fire, while the ship moves close to engage and ram the enemy ships. This makes it especially deadly against wooden warships.\nConstruction of these ship types requires mid-level (2) shipyards.
Ironclad Gunboat Rams available.

