Finance national communication that is primarily used to influence and persuade an audience to further the nation's agenda, which may not be objective and may be selectively presenting facts to encourage a particular synthesis or perception, or using loaded language to produce an emotional rather than a rational response to the information that is being presented. Some say propaganda, but we'll call it patriotic reporting of the facts, our loyal citizens being the target audience.\nEach level of this project will further increase support in loyal states.
Support in loyal states


